Alder is an open-source android note taking application which provides a user with simplicity as well as productivity. It comes with a clean materialistic design.

It was built by Zlifno and its provided at no cost.

Alongside being able to create and edit notes, there is the option for an image note which is to be added soon.

Features

*Quick and simple note editor

*Ability to add, delete and edit notes

*Material design

*Fast scrubbing through list

*Focused on design

*Open-source

*More features coming soon


With the light, intuitive and easy to use features of Alder, it is the note taking application for the job!
